---
title: Vietnamese Double Chicken Bowls with Quick-Pickled Veggies
description: Experience the vibrant flavours of Vietnam-inspired cuisine with this bowl! Succulent chicken glazed in a Nuoc Cham sauce served atop fragrant jasmine rice. Accompanied by quick-pickled cucumber for a refreshing crunch, it's a tantalizing fusion of sweet, savoury, and tangy flavours in every bowlful.
